Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:23.43,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fsp-1\blur2.5}揺れた　現実感　なくしたままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:28.43,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fsp-1\blur2.5}瓦礫のように　積み重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.45,0:01:32.64,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fsp-1\blur2.5}この感傷はどこへ行く？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:35.02,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fsp-1\blur2.5}潰えた希望抱え
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:39.52,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fsp-1\blur2.5}赤い雨を払い走った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:42.94,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fsp-1\blur2.5}夢中に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:49.68,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fsp-1\blur2.5}崩れた　感情の果てに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:50.91,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fsp-1\blur2.5}何を見る？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:52.08,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fsp-1\blur2.5}何がある？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:53.75,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fsp-1\blur2.5}まだ知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:59.73,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\fsp-1\blur2.5}儚い　全ての未来は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:08.81,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,600)\fsp-1\blur2.5}ただ無音に　目の前に　広がり続けた
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================================================================================ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:07.30,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-2}「もう闇が終わる」と
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:14.30,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-2}暗く淀む　君の目が呟く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.30,0:21:18.33,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-2}ただ　崩れた世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:25.12,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-2}明日への行き場すら無くして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:31.96,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-2}だけど　守るべき人　声が導く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.98,0:21:38.87,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-2}涙をもう見ないと決めた時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:42.84,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-2}心の枷　壊して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:50.93,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-2}今　凍える心を　炎で融かし
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.96,0:21:55.07,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-2}銃把を握り締め
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:59.94,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-2}今　震える指を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.95,0:22:06.50,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-2}銃爪の黒に　強く宛がう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:19.12,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-2}この　命をただ　狂気の弾に　変えて
